#: user/serializers.py:226
msgid "Spark: Account Activation"
msgstr "Spark：アカウントの有効化"

#: user/templates/user/emails/activation_email.html:5
msgid "Welcome to Spark,"
msgstr "Sparkへようこそ、"

#: user/templates/user/emails/activation_email.html:8
msgid ""
"We are thrilled to have you here. To start swiping and finding your perfect "
"match, please activate your account by clicking the button below."
msgstr ""
"Sparkへようこそ！スワイプを始めて理想の相手を見つけるために、下のボタンをク"
"リックしてアカウントを有効化してください。"

#: user/templates/user/emails/activation_email.html:15
msgid "Activate Account"
msgstr "アカウントを有効化する"

#: user/templates/user/emails/activation_email.html:22
msgid "If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:"
msgstr ""
"ボタンが正しく動作しない場合は、以下のリンクをブラウザにコピー＆ペーストして"
"ください："

#: user/templates/user/emails/base_email.html:29
msgid "Connecting hearts through technology."
msgstr "テクノロジーで心を繋ぐ。"

#: user/templates/user/emails/base_email.html:32
msgid "All rights reserved."
msgstr "All rights reserved. (著作権所有)"

#: user/templates/user/emails/reset_password_email.html:5
msgid "Password Reset Request"
msgstr "パスワード再設定のリクエスト"

#: user/templates/user/emails/reset_password_email.html:8
msgid ""
"We received a request to reset the password for your Spark account. If you "
"didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email."
msgstr ""
"Sparkアカウントのパスワード再設定のリクエストを受け付けました。もし心当たりが"
"ない場合は、このメールを無視していただいて構いません。"

#: user/templates/user/emails/reset_password_email.html:15
msgid "Reset Password"
msgstr "パスワードを再設定する"

#: user/templates/user/emails/reset_password_email.html:22
msgid "This link will expire soon for your security."
msgstr "セキュリティ保護のため、このリンクの有効期限はまもなく切れます。"

#: user/views.py:454
msgid "Spark: Password Recovery"
msgstr "Spark：パスワードの再設定"